    <briefdescription>
<para>Renders scenes through their configured viewports. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This system iterates over all active viewport IDs from the session, resolves the associated scene and viewport via <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1modules_1_1scene_1_1types_1_1SceneToViewportMap" kindref="compound">SceneToViewportMap</ref>, creates a scene snapshot, and submits it to the rendering device.</para>
<para>The system runs in the Post phase after all gameplay updates are complete, ensuring the scene graph reflects the final state for this frame.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1modules_1_1scene_1_1types_1_1SceneToViewportMap" kindref="compound">SceneToViewportMap</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>RenderingDevice </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para>RenderPassFactory </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
